1
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:12,240
Not bad.

2
00:00:13,320 --> 00:00:15,320
Since the Princess is from Beidi,

3
00:00:15,320 --> 00:00:17,040
she naturally speaks the language.

4
00:00:17,040 --> 00:00:19,080
We hope the Princess can use the Beidi language

5
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:20,340
to prove her innocence

6
00:00:20,640 --> 00:00:22,480
and clear His Majesty's doubts.

7
00:00:30,840 --> 00:00:31,760
How dare you!

8
00:00:33,400 --> 00:00:35,120
How dare you slander the Princess

9
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:37,050
and shift the blame to His Majesty?

10
00:00:37,600 --> 00:00:40,120
What are your intentions, Lord Gu?

11
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:45,760
Su Cheng, Vice Minister of Revenue, pays respects to Your Majesties.

12
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:47,020
Greetings, Princess.

13
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,360
Su Cheng.

14
00:00:49,760 --> 00:00:50,880
You may rise.

15
00:00:52,400 --> 00:00:53,800
Thank you, Your Majesty.

16
00:00:57,080 --> 00:01:00,840
Just now, Lord Gu proposed verifying the Princess's identity.

17
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,800
I think it is permissible.

18
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:05,000
If the Princess fails the verification,

19
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:06,880
it's the crime of deceiving the monarch,

20
00:01:06,880 --> 00:01:08,240
and she should be executed.

21
00:01:08,240 --> 00:01:10,320
But if she passes,

22
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:13,400
then Lord Gu and his wife are guilty of slandering the Princess,

23
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,730
and they deserve to die.

24
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:19,400
My wife and I can share the burden of the state,

25
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:22,200
and we will die without regrets.

26
00:01:31,640 --> 00:01:34,560
This is the bilateral treaty I drafted recently.

27
00:01:35,280 --> 00:01:37,880
Please translate it for us, Princess.

28
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:40,080
If there is even the slightest mistake,

29
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:42,890
I beseech Your Majesty to make a judgment.

30
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,979
Your Majesty of Beidi,

31
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:47,080
what

32
00:01:47,440 --> 00:01:48,560
do you think?

33
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:49,880
I will defer to my host.

34
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,120
Let's do as he says.

35
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,560
Okay.

36
00:02:03,840 --> 00:02:06,100
Do you still remember that little mouse?

37
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,040
I tricked you.

38
00:02:21,079 --> 00:02:22,120
Come catch me.

39
00:02:22,720 --> 00:02:23,720
You are so bad.

40
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:24,780
You can't catch me.

41
00:02:25,760 --> 00:02:26,400
Stop running.

42
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:27,660
Come here and catch me.

43
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:30,000
Yu,

44
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:31,720
is it really you?

45
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:40,160
Princess, my daughter.

46
00:02:40,600 --> 00:02:41,800
Summon the imperial physician!

47
00:02:41,800 --> 00:02:43,060
Summon the physician!

48
00:02:54,320 --> 00:02:56,440
What is wrong with the Princess?

49
00:02:56,440 --> 00:02:58,360
Please tell us the truth, Imperial Physician.

50
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,280
The Princess

51
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,400
has a weak pulse

52
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,920
and depleted qi and blood.

53
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:03,600
I don't know the cause.

54
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,280
But it's not a serious illness.

55
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:07,600
She'll be fine after a short rest.

56
00:03:09,120 --> 00:03:10,520
In that case,

57
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:12,480
we shouldn't disturb her rest.

58
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:15,400
We will verify it after she wakes up.

59
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:21,520
I doubt you can pull any tricks in such a short time.

60
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,560
It should be so.

61
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,040
Since that is the case,

62
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,880
Your Majesty of Beidi,

63
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:28,440
please accompany me back to the main hall

64
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:30,370
to discuss the alliance in detail.

65
00:03:49,480 --> 00:03:50,400
What should I do?

66
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:51,280
You can hide for a while,

67
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,520
but you can't hide forever.

68
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,680
Time is running out.

69
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:55,079
Hurry up and memorize it.

70
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,960
Memorizing Beidi language from a dictionary now,

71
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:07,760
how is that possible?

72
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,620
It's impossible for anyone else,

73
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,640
but for you...

74
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,720
Does the pill book record

75
00:04:14,720 --> 00:04:16,680
a pill that can improve memory?

76
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,000
Huixin Pill.

77
00:04:24,680 --> 00:04:26,400
How do you know about the pill book?

78
00:04:26,400 --> 00:04:27,560
Are you really Yu?

79
00:04:27,840 --> 00:04:29,370
It's not the right time yet.

80
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,960
Whatever you want to say,

81
00:04:31,520 --> 00:04:33,120
we will talk after we escape.

82
00:04:58,400 --> 00:05:00,920
Since the princess is feeling better,

83
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:03,360
please begin.

84
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,200
Mother, please take a look,

85
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,680
and see if my translation is correct.

86
00:05:35,680 --> 00:05:38,159
(In Beidi) Are you feeling better, my daughter?

87
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:40,560
(In Beidi) I'm fine now. Thank you, Mother.

88
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:44,240
How is it?

89
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:46,880
Do you want me to read it to you again in Beidi?

90
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,560
Don't push me too far.

91
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,760
I married my daughter into Great Jin

92
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,920
not to be humiliated by others.

93
00:05:58,159 --> 00:06:00,820
I will definitely seek justice for this matter.

94
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,920
Your Majesty,

95
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,160
Gu Licheng and his wife committed insubordination,

96
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,240
slandered the princess,

97
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,560
and damaged the alliance between the two countries.

98
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:10,360
They deserve the death penalty.

99
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:13,400
Please make a decision, Your Majesty.

100
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,920
How dare you, Gu Licheng!

101
00:06:17,920 --> 00:06:18,640
Do you plead guilty?

102
00:06:18,640 --> 00:06:21,440
Your Majesty, have mercy! Please spare our lives!

103
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:25,720
Today, in front of the Emperor of Beidi,

104
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:27,040
you disgraced our country

105
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,160
and disregarded the alliance between our two countries.

106
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,890
Your crimes are unforgivable.

107
00:06:31,520 --> 00:06:33,240
Since Ayu is not dead,

108
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,840
I don't have to kill out of hatred.

109
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,480
Guards!

110
00:06:41,159 --> 00:06:42,040
Wait.

111
00:06:44,240 --> 00:06:45,520
Your Majesty,

112
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,920
although they offended me,

113
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,980
shedding blood would hurt the harmony of our alliance.

114
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,960
Please have mercy, Your Majesty,

115
00:06:52,960 --> 00:06:54,280
and spare their lives.

116
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,840
Emperor of Beidi,

117
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:58,860
the princess is very sensible

118
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,200
and considers the alliance between our two countries.

119
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:02,400
It is truly

120
00:07:02,680 --> 00:07:04,540
a blessing for our two countries.

121
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:07,740
You flatter me, Emperor of Great Jin.

122
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:12,840
Princess, in that case,

123
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,880
I will leave them to you.

124
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:18,720
Thank you, Your Majesty.

125
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,080
Get up.

126
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:36,400
What kind of trick are you playing?

127
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:38,000
You can be spared from death,

128
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,650
but you cannot escape punishment.

129
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:48,560
Mu Jiuyun,

130
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,490
I will definitely kill you!

131
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:11,290
Bo Baorui

132
00:08:14,240 --> 00:08:14,600
Zhong Xiaqiang

133
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,460
Zhong Xiaqiang

134
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,420
Zi Jianqiangqipin

135
00:08:17,840 --> 00:08:18,160
Quan Xuhang

136
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:18,820
Quan Xuhang

137
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,400
Quan Yulong

138
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,060
Quan Yulong

139
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:21,280
Licheng Lefei

140
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,520
Yunlong Yinyujia Guangjing

141
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:26,520
Luo Xiaocong Lin Xunbo

142
